This piece is a cinematic interpretation of discovery, shifting the meaning of value from material wealth to technological evolution.

Set within a journey of exploration, it carries a deeper message: the true significance lies not in what is found, but in what is being built.

@GenLayer represents part of that future, where innovation, intelligence, and emerging digital systems redefine what value means.

Note on representation:
The figures shown are symbolic storytelling elements and are not intended as literal portrayals or endorsements.

